 of the government.", "last_comment_created": 1774808403960, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": true, "comments": 7, "score_up": 28, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2038227984692257038", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ8G4iK8", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 41, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8521480, "raw_content": "", "author": "Belleoffreedom", "created": 1774797596864, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Valiazaner", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZ8G4iK8.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/Jkylebass/status/2038227984692257038?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "J-20 Fighter jet's chief Designer Yang Wei found dead", "last_comment_created": 1774799345341, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 41, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": [{"width": 715, "heightRatio": 81, "url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HEgLCRgaEAAc9K_.jpg", "height": 584}], "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 0, "created": 1774706043000, "id": "2037890969476231444", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1284500791252750337/2K90dEu3_normal.jpg", "displayName": "Taiwan Military", "username": "TaiwanMilitary"}, "content": "Reportedly, Yang was probed after \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\uddf3\u2019s JY-series anti-stealth radars sold to \ud83c\uddfb\ud83c\uddea & \ud83c\uddee\ud83c\uddf7 proved ineffective. \ud83c\udde8\ud83c\uddf3 had used the J-20 as a test target & falsely told Xi the radars could detect \ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 F-35 & F-22 stealth jets. This raised doubts about the J-20\u2019s claimed stealth capabilities.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 1281}, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 147, "created": 1774786394000, "id": "2038227984692257038", "video": false, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1807806285951508480/p-jDZAXK_normal.jpg", "displayName": "\ud83c\uddfa\ud83c\uddf8 Kyle Bass \ud83c\uddf9\ud83c\uddfc", "username": "Jkylebass"}, "content": "After U.S. forces turned China\u2019s most advanced anti-stealth radar\u2014the JY-27A\u2014into little more than lawn art, Xi reportedly ordered the execution of its chief designer, Yang Wei. Engineering with Chinese characteristics\u2026", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2310}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ8G49pJ", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 61, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8521221, "raw_content": "", "author": "DebunkTheLeft", "created": 1774789713613, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "ColonelKlink", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "www.zerohedge.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZ8G49pJ.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://www.zerohedge.com/geopolitical/uks-ofcom-investigate-complaints-climate-change-denial", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "UK will now police \"climate change denial\"", "last_comment_created": 1774813683402, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 8, "score_up": 61, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"description": "ZeroHedge - On a long enough timeline, the survival rate for everyone drops to zero", "large_image": "cHknfHcMvZyyyaul.png", "title": "UK's Ofcom To Investigate Complaints Of Climate-Change Denial"}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZ8G652K", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 23, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8521904, "raw_content": "DIVINE GOVERNMENT                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                                                          \nOn the first anniversary of the Battle of Lexington - the beginning of the American Revolution - local pastor Jonas Clarke preached a sermon.  He spoke eloquently about God's overruling providence.  He said, \"Next to the acknowledgement of the existence of a Deity, there is no one principle of greater importance in religion, than a realizing belief of the divine government and providence... That God is Governor among the nations, that His government is wise and just, and that all our times and changes are in His hands.                                                                                                                   \n                                                                                                                                            \nWe are not waiting for God to take control.  He is already in control.  When we see the chaos of our world today, we may be tempted to despair.  But things are not what they seem.                                                                                             \n                                                                                                                                            \nThe same God who governs the galaxies is overseeing the times - and He ordains all our steps as well.  His throne is in heaven, and earth is His footstool.                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n                                                                                                                                       \nGive thanks today that Jesus Christ is now and forever Lord of ALL.", "author": "Rosebud4Jesus", "created": 1774808715301, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Agent_86", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "DAILY VERSE: Thus says the Lord: \"Heaven is My throne, and earth is My footstool.\"  ISAIAH 66:1", "last_comment_created": 1774808925677, "content": "<p>DIVINE GOVERNMENT</p>\n<p>On the first anniversary of the Battle of Lexington - the beginning of the American Revolution - local pastor Jonas Clarke preached a sermon.  He spoke eloquently about God's overruling providence.  He said, &quot;Next to the acknowledgement of the existence of a Deity, there is no one principle of greater importance in religion, than a realizing belief of the divine government and providence... That God is Governor among the nations, that His government is wise and just, and that all our times and changes are in His hands.</p>\n<p>We are not waiting for God to take control.  He is already in control.  When we see the chaos of our world today, we may be tempted to despair.  But things are not what they seem.</p>\n<p>The same God who governs the galaxies is overseeing the times - and He ordains all our steps as well.  His throne is in heaven, and earth is His footstool.</p>\n<p>Give thanks today that Jesus Christ is now and forever Lord of ALL.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 1, "score_up": 23, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2038283360569540832", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASZ8G65Im", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 22, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8521940, "raw_content": "", "author": "Crucible", "created": 1774809581167, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "DontBeAFaggot", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASZ8G65Im.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/ShadowofEzra/status/2038283360569540832?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "The bombing of Tel Aviv will continue until morale improves", "last_comment_created": 1774815958749, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 22, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_sta